      Xie, Yuwei  and
      Challis, Jonathan K.  and
      Ankley, Phillip J.  and
      Brinkmann, Markus  and
      Jones, Paul D.  and
      Giesy, John P.",
    journal = "Science of The Total Environment, Volume 807",
